---
<section class="py-20 bg-white px-6 border-b border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Promise To You</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        When we step onto your property, your family's safety and well-being becomes our #1 priority. A roof isn't just shingles and nails—it's the shield that protects everything you love. We don't cut corners because we treat your home like our own.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div class="p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 text-[#E1251B] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Licensed & Insured</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Fully licensed to operate in Florida. We carry comprehensive insurance so you never have to worry.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 text-[#E1251B] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Local Riverview Crews</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">We live here. We work here. We aren't packing up and leaving town after storm season ends.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 text-[#E1251B] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Honest Inspections</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">If you just need a repair, we'll tell you. We don't push replacements on roofs that have years of life left.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>